      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still carries a deep luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small door ding on the passenger side consistent with careful use. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, with all electronic features and climate control systems functioning as they should. Mechanically, the car is sound and drives smoothly, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
