    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "This is a fantastic find for anyone seeking a reliable and well-maintained vehicle! It's in great shape overall and has clearly been looked after, offering a smooth and comfortable ride. While you'll find some light signs of previous adventures, it remains a sharp-looking car that's ready for many more miles of dependable service!",
